/.idea/
.DS_Store

# Repo agent runtime dir at repo root only (bootstrap output; see `bootstrap-ai-playbook` skill)
/.ai-playbook/
# Legacy committed repo facts paths (deny accidental re-commit after migration)
/docs/facts.md
/docs/maintenance/facts.md
/docs/reviews

# Ephemeral session scratch (see docs/AGENTS.md)
/docs/tmp/

# Repo-root scripts/ is local-only (hygiene runner lives in ~/.ai-playbook/scripts/)
/scripts/

